积极”信息时说道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>将其可能收购<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">动视暴雪</a>的最后期限延长至<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsofts-activision-acquisition-gets-october-deadline-3470491">10 月</a>，以争取英国竞争和市场管理局的支持。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-witcher-voice-actor-doug-cockle-opens-up-about-cancer-diagnosis-3470521">《巫师》配音演员道格·科克尔 (Doug Cockle) 发表的有关癌症诊断的帖子首先出现</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
这部宗教惊悚片出人意料地成为夏季最热门的电影之一https://www.nme.com/news/film/sound-of-freedom-religious-thriller-unexpected-hit-biggest-movies-3470507?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sound-of-freedom-religious-thriller-意想不到的热门大电影Hollie GeraghtyWed, 19 Jul 2023 15:36:39 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3470507 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="自由之声依旧" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《自由之声》也被网络阴谋论所纠缠</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sound-of-freedom-religious-thriller-unexpected-hit-biggest-movies-3470507">这部宗教惊悚片出人意料地成为今年夏季最大的电影之一，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="自由之声依旧" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/sound-of-freedom-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《自由之声》是</em>一部新的宗教惊悚片，讲述了一名特工执行儿童拐卖案件救援任务的故事，该片出人意料地成为夏季热门影片。</p><p>这部电影也与网络阴谋论纠缠在一起，但取得了票房成功，票房收入达 8500 万美元（6500 万英镑）。</p><p> <em>《自由之声》的</em>灵感来自于前国土安全部特工蒂姆·巴拉德（吉姆·卡维泽饰演）的经历，他花了十多年的时间捣毁儿童贩卖团伙。</p><p>影片简介如下：“一个令人难以置信的真实故事，讲述了一名前政府特工变成义务警员，开始执行一项危险的任务，从性贩运者手中解救数百名儿童。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="自由之声 - 官方预告片 (2023)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rt0kp4VW1cI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2023/jul/06/sound-of-freedom-movie-qanon-jim-caviezel" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《卫报》</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/tv-movies/tv-movie-reviews/sound-of-freedom-jim-caviezel-child-trafficking-qanon-movie-1234783837/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《滚石》</a></em>分别将这部电影描述为 QAnon 的“邻近”和“带点色彩”的惊悚片——指的是美国极右翼阴谋论，即一些最糟糕的最有权势的政治和文化精英从事人口贩运，恋童癖、虐待儿童和许多其他毫无根据的理论。</p><p>与这部电影相关的阴谋论包括右翼猜测，即 AMC 影院公司想要破坏放映。</p><p>正如<em><a href="https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20230714-sound-of-freedom-is-the-child-trafficking-drama-a-watershed-moment-for-faith-based-filmmaking" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC</a></em>指出的那样，对这部电影的一些负面报道也与卡维泽过去似乎接受了 QAnon 理论有关。</p><p>该片的发行商天使影业<a class="color-link" title="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/11/business/sound-of-freedom-trafficking.html" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/11/business/sound-of-freedom-trafficking.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" data-ga-track="ExternalLink:https://www.nytimes.com/2023/07/11/business/sound-of-freedom-trafficking.html" aria-label="denies">否认</a>该片与阴谋论有关，AMC 影院首席执行官亚当·阿伦也在推特上<a href="https://twitter.com/CEOAdam/status/1679212647772995586?s=20">封杀了与影院放映相关的理论</a>。</p><p>一些观众还将《自由之声》解读为一部“基于信仰的电影”。</p><p>尽管围绕着阴谋论，这部电影的票房表现不错，但评价却褒贬不一。</p><p> <em><a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/reviews/sound-of-freedom-review-jim-caviezel-1235660035/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《综艺》杂志</a></em>将其描述为“一部引人入胜的电影，真实地揭示了我们这个时代最重要的犯罪恐怖事件之一，而好莱坞大多对此避而不谈”。</p><p>然而， <em><a href="https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/sound-of-freedom-movie-review-2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RogerEbert.com</a></em>表示这部电影是“严肃而冗长的无聊”。</p><p> <em><a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/tv-movies/tv-movie-reviews/sound-of-freedom-jim-caviezel-child-trafficking-qanon-movie-1234783837/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《滚石》</a></em>将<em>《自由之声》</em>描述为“一部为患有脑虫的爸爸们准备的超级英雄电影”，并补充道，“这部关于贩卖儿童的不带QA色彩的惊悚片旨在唤起一个被阴谋困扰的婴儿潮一代的良心”。</p><p>目前该片在烂番茄上的影评人评分为73%，观众评分为100%。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sound-of-freedom-religious-thriller-unexpected-hit-biggest-movies-3470507">这部宗教惊悚片出人意料地成为今年夏季最大的电影之一，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
